@startuml
title HÌNH 3.4: Vòng đời JIT credential (Vault)
caption Label: fig:vault_jit_lifecycle

' Tùy chỉnh để chiều ngang hẹp lại
skinparam MaxMessageSize 150
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

box "Kubernetes Cluster" #AliceBlue
    participant "Mutating\nWebhook" as K8s
    participant "vault-agent\n(Init/Sidecar)" as Agent
    participant "tmpfs\n(Shared Vol)" as Tmpfs
    participant "env-loader\nwatcher" as Loader
    participant "App\nContainer" as App
end box

box "Security & Storage" #GhostWhite
    participant "HashiCorp\nVault" as Vault
    database "MySQL\nDatabase" as MySQL
end box

== 1. Khởi tạo & Định danh ==
K8s -> Agent : 1. Pod Created\nInject vault-agent
|||
Agent -> Vault : 2. Auth via\nK8s SA Token
|||

== 2. Cấp phát Quyền hạn (JIT) ==
Vault -> MySQL : 3. CREATE USER 'usr_random'\nGRANT SELECT, INSERT,\nUPDATE, DELETE
|||
Vault -> Agent : 4. Send Creds:\n{user, pass, lease_id,\nduration=3600}
|||

== 3. Chuyển giao Secrets ==
Agent -> Tmpfs : 5. Write to\n/vault/secrets/.env.db
|||
Loader -> Tmpfs : 6. Merge .env files\n-> /app-secrets/.env
|||
App -> Loader : 7. Read .env &\nConnect MySQL
|||

== 4. Tái cấp phát & Cập nhật (Loop) ==
loop Khi TTL hết hạn (Expires)
    Agent -> Vault : 8. Renew/Re-fetch\ncredentials
    |||
    Vault -> MySQL : 9. DROP 'old_user'\nCREATE 'new_user'
    |||
    Agent -> Tmpfs : Update .env.db
    |||
    Loader -> App : 10. Detect change\nCall /reload-db
    |||
    App -> MySQL : Re-connect with\nNew Credentials
end
@enduml